# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Field gun platoons crew heavy ultra autocannons that can fire at twice the normal rate, delivering devastating bursts of heavy-caliber fire that can cripple vehicles and stagger BattleMechs. The double-rate fire comes at the cost of increased jamming risk, and the heavy ammunition consumption demands well-stocked supply lines. These platoons pack the firepower of much larger formations when the mechanism functions reliably, but a jam at the wrong moment can leave the crew defenseless.</p>
</overview>

